data.description: Welcome to 9914 Grayson Gardens Dr, a stunning single-family property that has it all! This contemporary home boasts 4 spacious bedrooms and 2 modern bathrooms, perfect for the whole family. With 2040 square feet of living space, entertaining guests or relaxing in style is a breeze. Built in 2016, this home showcases a contemporary charm that is sure to impress. The 6000 square foot lot offers ample space for outdoor activities and gardening. The neighborhood is a true gem, featuring a pool, basketball court, and park, providing endless recreational options. The unique layout, with houses surrounded by gardens rather than directly facing each other, creates a serene and pleasant living environment. Don't wait, this beautiful property is priced at $369,995 and won't stay on the market for long!
